    <metadata>
        <name>La Berra via Hauta Chia and La Valsainte</name>
        <desc>Get away from the crowd and enjoy the opportunity to discover some of the pastures of the Javro valley. This is a mid-altitude mountain walk without any technical difficulties but with a fair amount of difference in height.</desc>
